          <p><a href="https://b35d31f38bf146ceab70f1bfc3b4f541.vfs.cloud9.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/reports/result">今月のレポート</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

       <div class="card text-center">
        <div class="card-header">
          その他
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
         <button type="button" class="btn btn-info"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> 資産運用シミュレーション</button>
         <button type="button" class="btn btn-info"><i class="fas fa-comment-dollar"></i> 貯金シミュレーション</button>
         <button type="button" class="btn btn-info"><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> 登録内容の編集</button>
        </div>
      </div>

     </div>
   </div>
